title: [CRASH] Crashed running the instuction at: 0x4b4377
body:
Redis 3 master 3 slave cluster, 192.168.241.78 node crash report at night is as follows:
It seems that the version we are using cannot be found officially. It may be a previous development version. I wonder if it is a known bug.
